WEBVTT

00:11:58.887 --> 00:12:01.244
Any technology
can be used for good or bad.

00:12:01.268 --> 00:12:03.680
Transparency to engagement
and effective regulation

00:12:03.704 --> 00:12:06.824
are absolutely critical
to building the trust for any of this.

00:12:08.106 --> 00:12:12.940
But the benefits that "empathetic
technology" can bring to our lives

00:12:12.964 --> 00:12:16.855
are worth solving the problems
that make us uncomfortable.

00:12:17.315 --> 00:12:21.340
And if we don't, there are
too many opportunities and feelings

00:12:21.364 --> 00:12:23.059
we're going to be missing out on.

00:12:23.083 --> 00:12:24.258
Thank you.

00:12:24.282 --> 00:12:26.761
(Applause)